      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scuffs and some minor paint fading on the roof and hood, while the interior shows moderate wear on the upholstery and a few cracked plastic trim pieces. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, but it will likely need routine maintenance items like new tires and a brake service in the near future. It is a solid, functional choice for someone looking for dependable transportation at an accessible price point.",
