    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this beauty. It's honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014absolutely flawless inside and out! I've babied this car since day one, and it still has that fresh new-car feel. It drives like an absolute dream and is looking for a new home where it'll be just as loved. If you're looking for perfection on wheels, this is the one! \u2728",
      "price": 44900.0,
