    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exceptional vehicle, maintained in impeccable showroom condition. This specimen has been curated with exacting standards, resulting in an aesthetic and mechanical state that is indistinguishable from new. From the flawless exterior luster to the pristine, untouched interior surfaces, every detail reflects a legacy of meticulous ownership and climate-controlled storage. This is a rare opportunity to acquire an investment-grade automobile that exceeds the expectations of the most discerning collector. Serious inquiries only.",
