      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this absolute gem! It\u2019s in stunning, showroom-ready condition and honestly looks like it just rolled off the lot. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for that 'brand new' feeling without the brand new price tag, this is the one you've been waiting for. Come take it for a spin\u2014you\u2019re going to love it!",
