      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered icon, preserved in showroom condition. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features individual throttle bodies and high-pressure double VANOS, delivering a razor-sharp throttle response and a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers precise shift throws, pairing perfectly with the variable M-differential for optimal torque distribution. The chassis is mechanically impeccable, featuring factory-correct suspension kinematics and documented preventative subframe reinforcement. With zero cosmetic blemishes and a pristine interior, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of early-2000s Bavarian engineering for the serious collector.",
